{"body": "Just a follow up, I didn't have time to benchmark the changes yet, I'll try to do in the following days.\r\n\r\nAnd a comment about calculating `@locals.keys` several times, I've talked to @josevalim and we confirmed that the proposed changes actually don't change the keys calculation, because they are default values for `find_template`, so they were being calculated on every `find_template` call without a second argument. Now they are just more explicit, with extra keys to make the object variable work.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5406984", "created_at": "2012-04-29T17:50:46Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6006#issuecomment-5406984", "updated_at": "2012-04-29T17:50:46Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6006, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52381041bd3543c15100d637